</li><li> In <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/Pacificators" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Webcomic/Pacificators">Pacificators</a></em>, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PlayingWithFire" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PlayingWithFire">Cinna</a> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FieryRedhead" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/FieryRedhead">Grossul</a> get to bust out a couple <a class="urllink" href="http://www.sailorenergy.net/MangaPacificators/MangaPacisV03CH01n184.html">awesome<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a> <a class="urllink" href="http://www.sailorenergy.net/MangaPacificators2/MangaPacisV04n110.html">ones<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>.
